# Comfort Fuel – Your Home, Your Health, Your Fuel!

## Overview

Comfort Fuel is a full-stack web application designed to connect customers with home-based food providers offering affordable, customizable, and nutritious meals.

The platform provides:

- A **Customer Portal** for browsing and ordering meals  
- A **Vendor Portal** for managing recipes and processing orders  
- Real-time chat between customers and vendors  
- Order tracking with status updates  
- Responsive UI with dark/light mode support  

The application is built using **React.js** and **Firebase**, and is deployed using **AWS Amplify** for cloud hosting and continuous deployment.

---

## Live Deployment

The application is deployed using AWS Amplify and is accessible at:

**https://<your-amplify-link>.amplifyapp.com**

